                            <h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-228_ pf-heading-1-h3">You are not starting over. You are learning how to lead your life differently.</h3>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-231_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Many women arrive here carrying full lives.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-233_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Responsibilities. Relationships. Work. Family. A mind that rarely stops. A constant awareness of what needs attention next.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-235_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">And while much of life may look good from the outside, internally there is often another truth:</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-237_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You feel stretched. A little disconnected. Often responsible for everyone and everything. Capable, but tired. Present physically, but not always fully inside your own life.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-239_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The problem is not that you are failing.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-235_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The problem is that somewhere along the way, you learned how to keep life moving, but not always how to remain deeply rooted while doing it.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-237_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Legacy of Beauty is where that begins to change.</p>
                            <a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-241_ btn-theme">I'M IN<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-242_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon"></i></a>
