                            <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-247_ pf-heading-1-h3">CHALLENGES YOU MAY BE FEELING:</h5>
                            <div class="lob-challenges-list">
                              <div class="lob-challenge-item">
                                <h3 class="lob-challenge-heading">Your mind rarely fully settles</h3>
                                <p class="lob-challenge-desc">Even when the day is ending, part of you is still mentally holding what needs attention next.</p>
                                <hr class="lob-challenge-divider" />
                              </div>
                              <div class="lob-challenge-item">
                                <h3 class="lob-challenge-heading">Your to-do list follows you everywhere</h3>
                                <p class="lob-challenge-desc">It is difficult to fully relax because something unfinished always seems to stay present in the background.</p>
                                <hr class="lob-challenge-divider" />
                              </div>
                              <div class="lob-challenge-item">
                                <h3 class="lob-challenge-heading">You feel stretched more easily than you want to</h3>
                                <p class="lob-challenge-desc">Small things can feel heavier than they should when your inner world already feels full.</p>
                                <hr class="lob-challenge-divider" />
                              </div>
                              <div class="lob-challenge-item">
                                <h3 class="lob-challenge-heading">Beauty often feels like something for later</h3>
                                <p class="lob-challenge-desc">The things that nourish you most are often the first things pushed aside when life gets busy.</p>
                                <hr class="lob-challenge-divider" />
                              </div>
                              <div class="lob-challenge-item">
                                <h3 class="lob-challenge-heading">You are present, but not always fully there</h3>
                                <p class="lob-challenge-desc">Even good moments can feel interrupted by the constant pull of what still needs managing.</p>
                                <hr class="lob-challenge-divider" />
                              </div>
                              <div class="lob-challenge-item">
                                <h3 class="lob-challenge-heading">Rest sometimes comes with guilt</h3>
                                <p class="lob-challenge-desc">Slowing down can feel harder than it should, even when you know you need it.</p>
