                        <div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:8;--c-lg:7">
                          <div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-263_">
                            <h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-264_ pf-heading-1-h3">I can help because I have been where you are.</h3>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-267_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Holding a lot. Thinking about many things at once. Caring deeply, showing up well, and still feeling the quiet weight of how much is always living in your mind.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-269_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You want your life to feel calmer, clearer, and more beautiful, but often it feels like your thoughts stay one step ahead of your ability to fully settle into the moment.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-271_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You may tell yourself you simply need to get more organized, more disciplined, or finally get everything in order.</p>
                            <h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-273_ pf-heading-1-h4">The truth?</h4>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-275_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">A full life does not become beautiful simply by managing it better.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-277_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">What began to change things for me was learning how to create rhythms that supported peace, structure that reduced inner noise, and practices that allowed me to become more present inside my own life.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-279_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This work is not about adding more to your list.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-281_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">It is about learning what belongs, what does not, and how to live in a way that creates greater steadiness, beauty, and peace over time.</p>
                            <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-282_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><strong>On the other side of this work, you begin to feel more at home in your own days.</strong></p>
                          </div>
                            </div>
