                                    <h1 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-294_ pf-heading-2-h3">WHO SHE IS COMING HOME TO?</h1>
                                    <h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-296_ pf-heading-7-h4">The woman whose life begins to feel more like her own again</h2>
                                  <ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:45px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eONOlN dawdJE pf-298_">
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-299_ pf-text-2"><strong>She no longer feels like her mind is carrying five things at once,</strong> even in the middle of a full day.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-301_ pf-text-2"><strong>Her presence feels calmer, steadier,</strong> and the people around her feel it too.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-303_ pf-text-2"><strong>Her mornings and evenings begin to feel less rushed,</strong> more intentional, and quietly life-giving.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-305_ pf-text-2"><strong>She makes decisions with more clarity</strong> and less inner back-and-forth.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-307_ pf-text-2"><strong>Her home begins to hold more warmth, beauty,</strong> and the kind of order that helps everyone breathe easier.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-309_ pf-text-2"><strong>She is less easily pulled into frustration, urgency, or emotional overreaction</strong> in the relationships that matter most.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-311_ pf-text-2"><strong>Rest begins to feel natural again</strong> instead of something she has to justify.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-313_ pf-text-2"><strong>She notices what her body needs</strong> before exhaustion forces her to pay attention.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-315_ pf-text-2"><strong>Things that once felt constantly heavy</strong> begin to feel lighter and more manageable.</li>
                                    <li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-317_ pf-text-2"><strong>She moves through her days with a deeper sense of peace, presence, and self-respect.</strong></li>
