                        <h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-336_">I used to think that living the life I truly desired would take so many years.</h2>
                        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-338_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">But then it began happening faster than I expected.</p>
                        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-340_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">I started getting more out of one year than I had in many before it, often because I learned how much can shift inside a focused 12-week season. I started thinking differently. Choosing differently. Living with more intention, more courage, and more willingness to move toward what I truly wanted.</p>
                        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-342_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">And listen, if you are thinking that some women simply have something special that you don’t, they do not.</p>
                        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-344_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">What often changes everything is a deeper desire for more and a willingness to keep showing up for the life you know is possible, one season at a time.</p>
                        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-346_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn">So if you are ready for a year where what you have imagined begins to take clearer shape in your real life, you are exactly where you need to be.</p>
                        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-347_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3" data-animation="fadeIn"><strong><em>You are closer than you think to living as the woman you have long wanted to become.</em></strong></p>
