          <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-461_ pf-heading-1-h3">This gets to be the kind of year where you feel yourself coming back to life in meaningful ways. More clear. More grounded. More present. More connected to and less pulled by the constant feeling that everything unfinished is quietly competing for your attention.</h5>
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0797/0390/0415/files/branding-55.jpg" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0797/0390/0415/files/branding-55.jpg 1536w" width="800" height="1200" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" data-pf-type="Image3" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-463_ pf-image-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"/>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-464_">
            <p>You get to become a woman who brings a different atmosphere with her. One who leads her days with greater intention, enjoys her home more, feels more at ease in her own skin, and notices that what once felt hard to hold is beginning to feel natural.</p>
            <p><b>We are not staying at the level of inspiration.</b> We are bringing thoughtful attention to the real places life is lived: your thoughts, your rhythms, your relationships, your desires, your emotional life, your calling, and the way beauty begins showing up in ordinary days.</p>
            <p>You also get to do this alongside women who care deeply about living well, growing honestly, and becoming more of who they were made to be.</p>
            <p>No more waiting for life to somehow feel different later. This is a year to participate in that now.</p>
          </div>
          <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-465_ pf-heading-1-h3">IF YOU WANT A HOLISTIC APPROACH TO HOW YOU LIVE, LOVE, LEAD, AND CREATE THE LIFE YOU DESIRE, YOU ARE IN THE RIGHT PLACE.</h5>
