          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-510_"><p><strong>Imagine ending the day with enough margin</strong> to light a candle, take a bath, linger over skincare, sit outside at sunset, or enjoy a quiet moment without feeling like you should be doing something else.</p></div>
          <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-511_ pf-heading-1-h3">ENERGY FOR WHAT BRINGS YOU JOY</h5>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-513_"><p><strong>Wouldn’t it feel good</strong> to cook something beautiful late in the evening, rearrange flowers on the counter, start a creative project, or finally read the book beside your bed because you are no longer running on empty.</p></div>
          <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-514_ pf-heading-1-h3">PEACE THAT CHANGES THE FEEL OF YOUR DAYS</h5>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-516_"><p><strong>To move through responsibilities without that constant undercurrent of pressure,</strong> and to notice that calm, steadiness, and enjoyment are becoming more natural.</p></div>
          <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-517_ pf-heading-1-h3">WARMTH AND CONNECTION IN YOUR RELATIONSHIPS</h5>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-519_"><p><strong>To feel more available, more affectionate, more present,</strong> and less mentally somewhere else when you are with the people you love.</p></div>
          <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-520_ pf-heading-1-h3">COMMUNITY THAT FEELS LIFE-GIVING</h5>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-522_"><p><strong>To be surrounded by women who care about beauty, growth, honesty, and living well,</strong> where conversation itself often opens new possibilities for your own life.</p></div>
            <a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-523_ pf-button-1">WAITLIST ME!<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-524_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon">
