<div data-section-id="pf-5959" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-527_ pf-color-scheme-1">
  <div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg">
    <div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-528_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row">
      <div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:7">
        <div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-529_">
          <h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-530_ pf-heading-1-h3">Imagine this...</h4>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-532_">
            <p><strong>You can almost picture it now:</strong> coming into the evening without feeling mentally pulled in five directions, the kitchen softly lit, dinner simple but beautiful, and your home feeling like a place you actually get to enjoy. Maybe there are flowers on the counter, candles lit, a favorite sweater on, and enough margin to sit down with tea before the night feels rushed.</p>
            <p><strong>Some nights you are finishing the dishes early</strong> and sitting down with a book, journaling, or watching something you enjoy because you are no longer trying to squeeze yourself into the very end of the day. Some nights you are lingering in conversation, preparing something thoughtful, or simply letting an ordinary evening feel slower and more intentional.</p>
            <p><strong>Imagine having the energy</strong> to invite people over on a weekday, to cook because you want to, to straighten a room because beauty matters to you, or to go to bed feeling settled instead of mentally unfinished.</p>
            <p>We have all lived the other way. It is not sustainable, and it does not create the kind of life most women are actually longing for.</p>
            <p><b>You want a life that feels beautiful to live, and you are allowed to build it.</b></p>
            <p><strong>This experience exists because meaningful change often happens</strong> when a woman has thoughtful guidance, honest reflection, and a place to keep showing up over time.</p>
            <p><strong>This is what it looks like to decide</strong> that a year from now your life will not simply look the same and feel heavier, but will carry more peace, clarity, and intention than it does today.</p>
        </div>
        <a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-533_ btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-534_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon">
