<div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-543_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row">
  <div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:5;--c-lg:5">
    <div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-544_">
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0797/0390/0415/files/branding-50.jpg" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0797/0390/0415/files/branding-50.jpg 1536w" width="1500" height="2251" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="Lori cooking with family" data-pf-type="Image3" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-545_ pf-image-1"/>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:7;--c-lg:7">
    <div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-546_">
      <h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-547_ pf-heading-1-h3">Creating the life you want to live can begin feeling far more possible than you think.</h4>
      <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-549_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Gone are the days of carrying everything with the same inner pressure and believing that peace has to wait until life is less full. As you begin living with greater clarity, steadier rhythms, and more honest attention to what is shaping you, a different way of living begins to take hold. You become a woman who is thoughtful with her energy, present in her relationships, and able to hold responsibility without constantly feeling consumed by it.</p>
    <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-551_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><em>The Legacy of Beauty</em> is a holistic experience designed to help you strengthen the inner life and the outer life together, so that what is changing within you begins to influence how you love, lead, choose, respond, and create the life you are living.</p>
    <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-553_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">You can expect your days to feel calmer, your home to feel more intentional, your relationships to feel more connected, your emotional life to become steadier, and your sense of purpose to grow clearer as the year unfolds.</p>
    <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-555_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The life you want does not happen because circumstances suddenly cooperate. <strong>It happens because you begin making choices that support what you desire, again and again, until what once felt difficult begins to feel like the way you live.</strong></p>
  <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-557_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">It is not effortless becoming the woman you want to be, but it is deeply worth choosing.</p>
  <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-559_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">So let this be the year you begin making decisions your future self will be thankful you made.</p>
<a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-561_ btn-theme">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-562_ pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon">
