            <h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-601_ pf-heading-1-h3">This is a <span style="font-style: italic;">YEAR-LONG EXPERIENCE:</span>
            <br>12 months of moving intentionally through the areas of life that shape how you live, relate, choose, lead, and create. Nothing stays at the surface, because meaningful change rarely happens when only one part of life is addressed.</h4>
            <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-603_">
              <p>I created <em>The Legacy of Beauty</em> because I know what can happen when a woman has thoughtful support over time, not just inspiration for a moment.</p>
              <p>This kind of container means you are not simply hoping life feels different a year from now.</p>
              <p>You are deciding to participate in that change while life is actually unfolding.</p>
              <p>You are deciding that this year will not simply pass, but will become a year where beauty begins taking clearer shape.</p>
            </div>
        <p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-604_" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Over time, you may notice everything beginning to shift:</p>
