                <h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-626_ pf-heading-1-h3">The Legacy of Beauty is for the woman who is ready to live differently. This is not for the woman who only wants to think about change and hope life feels different later. This is for the woman who is willing to look honestly at how she is living, take responsibility for what is shaping her days, and begin making thoughtful choices that support her experience and her legacy.</h3>
