            <i>finally</i> commit to:</h4>
            <div class="lob-collage">
              <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0797/0390/0415/files/branding-10.jpg" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0797/0390/0415/files/branding-10.jpg 1536w" width="1500" height="2250" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, calc(100vw/3)" loading="lazy" alt="Intentional living" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-690_ pf-image-1 lob-collage-main"/>
