            <h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-692_ pf-heading-1-h3">The Legacy of Beauty is for the woman who...</h4>
            <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-694_"><p><strong>Is holding many roles at once</strong> and knows how quickly that can shape the feel of everyday life: from leading in her work, to caring for children or grandchildren, supporting a spouse, showing up for aging parents, carrying emotional responsibility in relationships, or simply being the one others often rely on.</p></div>
            <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-695_"><p><strong>Is leading in some area of life,</strong> whether that looks like running a business, managing a home, guiding a family through a demanding season, serving deeply in her community, or quietly making countless decisions that affect the people around her. If you are carrying responsibility for yourself or others in any capacity, this work is for you.</p></div>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-696_"><p><strong>Is ready to put down the quiet belief</strong> that exhaustion is just part of being capable.</p></div>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-697_"><p><strong>No longer wants to feel the pressure</strong> of always holding everything together internally.</p></div>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-698_"><p><strong>Wants to move through home, work, relationships, and personal life</strong> in a way that feels more spacious, thoughtful, and life-giving.</p></div>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-699_"><p><strong>Is tired of feeling like she is always catching up</strong> and wants life to feel more grounded, beautiful, and fully inhabited.</p></div>
          <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-700_"><p><strong>Needs real, honest, practical support</strong> that helps her live differently, because surface-level encouragement is no longer enough.</p></div>
