                                <h1 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-769_ pf-heading-1-h1">THE DETAILS</h1>
                                <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-771_">
                                  <h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;">
                                    <b>A 12-month guided experience.</b> Come with me through a full year of thoughtful growth, honest reflection, and intentional living as we move through the areas that most shape how a woman experiences her life. This is not built around surface motivation or quick fixes, but around learning how to live with greater clarity, steadiness, beauty, and presence while real life is happening.
                                  </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-772_">
                                  <h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;">
                                    <b>Monthly live teaching sessions.</b> Each month we gather for one focused teaching built around a meaningful area of life: emotional steadiness, identity, rhythms, relationships, desire, calling, home, peace, and the deeper patterns shaping how you live. Some teachings will introduce new ideas, while others will deepen what needs repeated attention because lasting change often comes through returning, not rushing.
                                  </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-773_">
                                  <h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;">
                                    <b>Guided coaching and reflection.</b> Alongside teaching, you will have space for thoughtful coaching conversations, journal prompts, and practical reflection so that what you are learning begins meeting your actual days. This is where insight becomes personal and usable.
                                  </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-774_">
                                  <h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;">
                                    <b>A community of thoughtful women.</b> One of the deepest parts of this experience is being among women who are also choosing to live more intentionally. Women carrying full lives, asking honest questions, noticing what matters, and learning how to create more beauty, peace, and clarity in the lives they already have.
                                  </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-775_">
                                  <h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;">
                                    <b>Seasonal movement through the year.</b> The year unfolds through four seasonal movements: She Awakens, She Knows, She Aligns, and She Lives. This gives the experience rhythm, depth, and language for the kind of growth that happens gradually and meaningfully over time.
                                  </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-776_">
                                  <h4 style="color:#FFF; font-weight: 400;">
                                    <b>Practical tools for real life.</b> You will not simply leave with ideas that sound beautiful. You will have language, reflection tools, and practices that support home life, emotional life, decision-making, relationships, and the ordinary places where life is actually being lived.
                                    <br><br>
                                    <b>Optional in-person gatherings and special experiences.</b> As this community grows, there may also be opportunities for in-person gatherings, seasonal events, or shared spaces that allow the work to move beyond the screen and into lived connection.
                                  </h4>
