                                                    <h5 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-879_ pf-heading-1-h3">YOUR GUIDE FOR THIS YEAR OF INTENTIONAL BECOMING</h5>
                                                    <h4 data-pf-type="Heading2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-881_ pf-heading-1-h3">Hi, I’m Lori. Your coach, teacher and guide for this year of intentional becoming.</h4>
                                                    <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-883_"><p>This 12-month guided experience, <em>The Legacy of Beauty</em>, is shaped by years of walking with women through the real work of growth: learning how to live with greater clarity, steadiness, beauty, and truth while carrying full lives, meaningful responsibilities, and the quiet complexity that often comes with both.</p></div>
                                                    <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-884_"><p>This work has also been shaped by my own life: building a home, raising a family, growing through changing seasons, leading in meaningful work, and learning again and again that beautiful living is not created by doing more, but by learning how to live more honestly and intentionally inside your lived legacy.</p></div>
                                                    <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-885_"><p>What I teach is not surface encouragement.</p></div>
                                                      <div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-gRtvfn YJaia pf-886_">
                                                        <p>It is thoughtful, practical formation that reaches the way you think, the way you respond, the way you structure your days, the way you care for relationships, and the way you begin creating a life that feels as meaningful on the inside as it may already look on the outside.</p>
                                                        <p>If you have spent time doing personal growth work before, this experience will deepen it by helping what you know become more lived, more integrated, and more visible in everyday life.</p>
                                                        <p><em>The Legacy of Beauty</em> is a year-long formation pathway for women who want growth to become more than something they understand, and begin becoming something they embody naturally over time.</p></div>
                                                        <a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-887_ pf-button-1 btn-theme pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide">JOIN THE WAITLIST<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-888_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon">
                                                        </i>
                                                      </a>
                                                      <a data-to-section="pf-cb45" data-offset="{&quot;all&quot;:50,&quot;laptop&quot;:50,&quot;tablet&quot;:50,&quot;mobile&quot;:50}" href="#" data-pf-type="Button2" data-animation="fadeIn" class="sc-emIqIH clWrLz pf-889_ pf-button-1 btn-theme">YES, I'M IN!<i class="sc-edLa-Dd cYbUCf pf-890_ pf-icon-1 pfa pfa-arrow-right" data-pf-type="Icon">
